Demon- (5)
- Starts the game with a Revive_Book, which is a role_item. This book can be used to revive any respawning player instantly. This book can only be used 3 times in a game.
- This book can also be used when the Demon is respawning.
- Reviving someone is an instant action. Has no cooldowns. (Can be used multiple times in 1 phase)
- Respawns in 4 phases.
